"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "6 月 25 日晚，杭州深度求索人工智能基础技术研究有限公司（下称 DeepSeek）发布招聘信息，表示正努力将所有部门的规模扩大至少一倍。DeepSeek 此次招聘涵盖 7 个大类的 33 个（类）岗位，工作地点为北京和杭州。 DeepSeek 大规模招聘: 至少扩大一倍 史上最大规模公开招募 DeepSeek 招聘"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-07f913d2b49bde68b0d4b18894fb1115.jpg?source=1a5df958"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "322 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2053625552725079594"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI2tP7ofXr85R2EAMaCTEyMDE0NzIwOSC2m/XRBjAAONYBQAJyEzIwNTM2MjU1NTI3MjUwNzk1OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1782483900.879489", "card_id": "Q_2053588599673549319", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "韩国队被曝发生内讧，金玟哉被换下后对教练组非常不满，是真的吗？韩国队内问题有多严重？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "世界杯韩国 0 比 1 爆冷不敌南非，金玟哉在下半场被换下后，对教练组非常不满。 此前队内风波: 2026 年世界杯 A 组关键战前，韩国队先乱了。自家媒体公然嘲讽队长孙兴慜，逼得随队新闻官辞职，全队已经全面封杀韩国本土媒体，闹出了世界杯开赛以来最离谱的队内风波。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6ba5602771dcaeaf75e5f47bc6b909e8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "250 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2053588599673549319"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI2tP7ofXr85R2EAMaCTEyMDE0NTQxNCDL1vTRBjAAOD1AA3ITMjA1MzU4ODU5OTY3MzU0OTMxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1782483900.879982", "card_id": "Q_2053058575203656580", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night